## Styling
- Tailwind CSS — dark mode default, cyberpunk/futuristic aesthetic
- Dark bg: `#0a0a0f` / `#0d0d1a`; Accent: cyan (`#00f5ff`) and purple (`#a855f7`)
- Framer Motion for animations; Lucide React for icons; shadcn/ui for components

## Commands

```bash
# Run from web-universe/ root
pnpm install
pnpm dev                          # starts all apps in parallel
pnpm --filter apps/web dev        # web only
pnpm --filter apps/marketplace dev  # marketplace only
pnpm build                        # production build
pnpm lint
```
